Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of MIMO techniques with OFDM for broadband wireless communication systems, which falls under the category of Information Theory (cs.IT) and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the use of precoding techniques to overcome the full diversity restriction issue, which falls under the category of Systems and Control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of beamforming and coding techniques for communication systems, which falls under the category of Communications (cs.COMM) and Multimedia (cs.MM).
